{"tid":2411694,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"由港股大龍市就睇得出，美股牛市已完","createTime":"2021-02-17T13:49:48.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-17T16:17:08.000Z","uid":219470,"like":6,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"905b659a17a0a39f379fcbfa20f323335c402c9f","tid":2411694,"uid":219470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T13:49:48.000Z","msg":"以前侵侵仲在位<br />\n有牙力勸掂國際投資者<br />\n叫佢地一齊煲大美國股市<br />\n<br />\n而家奶共登一上位<br />\n聽共產黨枝笛<br />\n叫埋國際投資者一齊運錢去白手套城市<br />\n咁先可以造就港股龍市<br />\n<br />\n正正係因為咁<br />\n港股先會登上位後一直升<br />\n美股一直妹甚至陰跌<br />\n<br />\n預計未來四年間情況會持續<br />\n換句話講<br />\n美股將會步入四年大熊市<br />\n大家睇路 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b79c9d23d23d0a24a6e6e91304d89c61083d303","tid":2411694,"uid":391931,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T13:52:59.000Z","msg":"一年前已經開始咁講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"937de78060ba92c5984c085ef9cb076c52878abb","tid":2411694,"uid":134908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T14:08:57.000Z","msg":"咩歌"},{"pid":"e40bfa38fa5e32c47f7e6cad23c31b041e5b7573","tid":2411694,"uid":45749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T14:16:25.000Z","msg":"龔成又贏"},{"pid":"3699da016d5c5ccea26b5def9169d9c4f073c32a","tid":2411694,"uid":356010,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T16:05:48.000Z","msg":"港股大龍市=2800"},{"pid":"fb8926385928d2d9198bdc5a3e92c234653107fa","tid":2411694,"uid":209853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T16:12:00.000Z","msg":"唔送<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db84d87f835666a4897249fb6d880783fb8b8bfe","tid":2411694,"uid":70888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T16:13:22.000Z","msg":"<img